1. Go to the Census API key registration page

Open: https://api.census.gov/data/key_signup.html

2. Fill out the registration form

Name: Your full name

Email: Your email (you’ll receive the key here)

Affiliation: Optional (like “Independent Researcher” or your company/university)

Reason for use: Short description, e.g., “Data analysis for research and visualization”

3. Submit the form

You’ll receive an API key via email almost instantly.
